But when I reached the hospital

10
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:29,579
and learned that you also
got in an accdient,

11
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:31,360
I really didn't know

12
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:32,220
how to tell you.

13
00:02:35,710 --> 00:02:37,240
That day, I had a dream,

14
00:02:40,150 --> 00:02:41,810
where you got injured as well.

15
00:02:44,310 --> 00:02:45,310
But later, you appeared

16
00:02:45,310 --> 00:02:47,040
at the hospital safe and sound.

17
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:50,240
So I didn't give it too much thought.

18
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:52,600
I didn't expect Shi Kai would...

19
00:02:53,150 --> 00:02:53,750
That's why

20
00:02:55,280 --> 00:02:57,480
I couldn't bring myself to utter a word.

21
00:02:57,590 --> 00:02:58,450
It was so cruel.

22
00:02:59,530 --> 00:03:00,790
I've even wondered...

23
00:03:01,120 --> 00:03:01,720
if there is

24
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:03,010
a connection

25
00:03:03,150 --> 00:03:03,840
between

26
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:05,710
Shi Kai's accident

27
00:03:06,590 --> 00:03:08,250
and the one you and Wei were in.

28
00:03:09,430 --> 00:03:11,030
But I checked multiple times

29
00:03:11,470 --> 00:03:13,330
and confirmed that your car crash

30
00:03:13,750 --> 00:03:15,080
was purely accidental.

31
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:17,000
Connection?

32
00:03:18,190 --> 00:03:20,800
Perhaps the connection
between these accidents

33
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:21,860
doesn't lie in you,

34
00:03:22,710 --> 00:03:23,630
but me.

35
00:03:24,280 --> 00:03:25,680
My appearance in this era

36
00:03:25,750 --> 00:03:27,150
is an accident itself.

37
00:03:27,680 --> 00:03:29,520
Will it bring more accidents

38
00:03:30,079 --> 00:03:31,410
to the people around me?

39
00:03:31,840 --> 00:03:32,370
Xiaolan.

40
00:03:34,240 --> 00:03:35,470
After the New Year,

41
00:03:36,079 --> 00:03:37,430
I may have to go back.

42
00:03:38,630 --> 00:03:39,680
Shi Kai's wife wanted

43
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:40,880
to work in Jingcheng.

44
00:03:41,430 --> 00:03:42,890
I helped her look for a job,

45
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:45,010
but problems occurred.

46
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:47,250
She refused to be transferred,

47
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:48,960
so I have to go back to her aid.

48
00:03:49,720 --> 00:03:50,560
Shi Kai was at work

49
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:52,420
with me when he had that accident.

50
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:54,850
I'd like to help his family
as much as I can.

51
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:57,730
Actually, I've also been thinking

52
00:03:58,470 --> 00:03:59,030
if I am

53
00:03:59,030 --> 00:04:00,630
getting a bit too involved.

54
00:04:04,750 --> 00:04:05,410
Zhou Cheng,

55
00:04:06,190 --> 00:04:08,190
I'm supportive of you helping them,

56
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:10,080
but there are boundaries.

57
00:04:11,030 --> 00:04:12,160
Think this through:

58
00:04:12,960 --> 00:04:13,870
