61
00:04:17,070 --> 00:04:18,510
for their future lives,

62
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:21,290
or because you hope to help them

63
00:04:21,510 --> 00:04:22,710
move on from the pain,

64
00:04:23,190 --> 00:04:24,510
and gradually become independent

65
00:04:24,510 --> 00:04:25,170
and strong?

66
00:04:25,190 --> 00:04:26,240
Of course I hope

67
00:04:26,270 --> 00:04:27,200
they can move on.

68
00:04:29,430 --> 00:04:30,960
Thank you for the reminder.

69
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:33,000
This time, I'll make sure

70
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:35,060
the matters are properly dealt with.

71
00:04:35,870 --> 00:04:36,930
Wait for my return.

72
00:04:38,750 --> 00:04:39,390
I will.

73
00:05:10,600 --> 00:05:11,070
Ms. Xia,

74
00:05:11,630 --> 00:05:12,750
I've brought you the car you booked

75
00:05:12,750 --> 00:05:13,560
