76
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:15,160
What a nice car.

77
00:05:15,480 --> 00:05:17,510
Ms. Xia, you've even bought a car.

78
00:05:17,870 --> 00:05:19,190
I see you're a big shot now.

79
00:05:19,190 --> 00:05:19,650
Come on,

80
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:21,250
