81
00:05:21,250 --> 00:05:21,780
Let's go.

82
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:22,510
Okay.

83
00:05:24,920 --> 00:05:27,120
Here, take a seat in the back, Granny Yu.

84
00:05:27,190 --> 00:05:28,630
Careful. Mind your head.

85
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:30,570
Okay.

86
00:05:31,560 --> 00:05:32,310
Thank you.

87
00:05:32,560 --> 00:05:33,220
Drive safe.

88
00:05:38,090 --> 00:05:40,350
Everyone gets a red envelope.
Wishing us a fruitful year ahead.

89
00:05:40,350 --> 00:05:41,400
Thanks, Ms. Bai.

90
00:05:41,430 --> 00:05:42,390
I wish you prosperity.

91
00:05:42,390 --> 00:05:44,159
-I wish you prosperity as well.
-Prosperity for everyone.

92
00:05:44,159 --> 00:05:45,360
Sis Bai, where's my red envelope?

93
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:48,310
Wishing you wealth
and success in all things.

94
00:05:48,510 --> 00:05:49,510
Thanks, Sis Bai.

95
00:05:49,510 --> 00:05:50,430
Here you are.

96
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:53,650
-Happy New Year!
-Happy New Year!

97
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:54,540
Happy New Year!

98
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:55,650
Thanks, Ms. Xia.

99
00:05:56,360 --> 00:05:57,040
Happy New Year, Ms. Xia.

100
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:58,070
Happy New Year to you too.

101
00:05:58,070 --> 00:05:58,750
Let it be a fantastic year.

102
00:05:58,750 --> 00:05:59,120
Thank you.

103
00:05:59,120 --> 00:05:59,600
Happy New Year.

104
00:05:59,600 --> 00:06:00,070
Thanks, Ms. Xia.

105
00:06:00,070 --> 00:06:01,720
Wishing us all a productive year.

106
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:02,270
Happy New Year.

107
00:06:02,270 --> 00:06:02,600
Thank you.

108
00:06:02,600 --> 00:06:03,360
Happy New Year.

109
00:06:03,360 --> 00:06:03,950
Thanks, Ms. Xia.

110
00:06:03,950 --> 00:06:05,160
Happy New Year.
Let there be a great start.

111
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:05,970
Is Chen in there?

112
00:06:05,970 --> 00:06:07,000
Yes, Mr. Chen is in his office.

113
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:07,400
Got it.

114
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:10,480
Chen,

115
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:11,410
Happy New...

116
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:12,860
Happy New Year.

117
00:06:13,510 --> 00:06:15,040
What happened to your face?

118
00:06:15,800 --> 00:06:16,830
N-N-Nothing.

119
00:06:17,310 --> 00:06:18,710
How is it nothing? You...

120
00:06:19,070 --> 00:06:20,470
I just didn't sleep well.

121
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:22,390
Is something wrong at home...

122
00:06:22,390 --> 00:06:23,190
Chen Xiliang!

123
00:06:24,680 --> 00:06:25,480
Chen Xiliang?

124
00:06:26,630 --> 00:06:27,360
It's my wife.

125
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:34,190
Honey.

126
00:06:36,070 --> 00:06:37,120
You have no shame,

127
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:37,800
Chen Xiliang.

128
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:38,480
I knew

129
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:39,310
you wouldn't suddenly

130
00:06:39,310 --> 00:06:40,950
open a factory in Shengcheng.

131
00:06:40,950 --> 00:06:41,720
Are you going to give

132
00:06:41,720 --> 00:06:43,070
all the money to this temptress?

133
00:06:43,070 --> 00:06:43,830
We'll talk at home.

134
00:06:43,830 --> 00:06:44,480
Stop yelling here.

135
00:06:44,480 --> 00:06:45,680
Listen, she's my business partner.

136
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:46,480
Business partner?

137
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:47,310
What business partner?

138
00:06:47,310 --> 00:06:48,520
I bet she's your sexual partner!

139
00:06:48,520 --> 00:06:49,600
You're a piece of filth!

140
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:50,630
Are you sleeping with...

141
00:06:50,630 --> 00:06:51,190
Stop it.

142
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:51,870
Chen Xiliang.

143
00:06:51,870 --> 00:06:52,430
Stop with this fuss!

144
00:06:52,430 --> 00:06:53,720
Explain the whole thing to your wife.

145
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:54,650
I'm leaving now.

146
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:55,360
Let go of me!

147
00:06:55,800 --> 00:06:56,750
Tell me what you've done!

148
00:06:56,750 --> 00:06:58,210
Enough. Get out of the way.

149
00:06:58,360 --> 00:06:58,830
This

150
00:06:58,830 --> 00:07:00,890
