151
00:07:01,120 --> 00:07:02,270
They are having an affair!

152
00:07:02,270 --> 00:07:03,310
Stop yelling here!

153
00:07:03,310 --> 00:07:04,160
How many times have I told you?

154
00:07:04,160 --> 00:07:05,310
She's a shareholder of my company.

155
00:07:05,310 --> 00:07:06,430
Stop being unreasonable.

156
00:07:06,430 --> 00:07:07,070
I'm telling you,

157
00:07:07,070 --> 00:07:07,630
at this rate,

158
00:07:07,630 --> 00:07:08,720
the trust between us will be gone,

159
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:09,920
and I'll divorce you!

160
00:07:12,430 --> 00:07:13,230
Chen Xiliang,

161
00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:14,510
divorce her or not—

162
00:07:14,510 --> 00:07:15,630
it has nothing to do with me.

163
00:07:15,630 --> 00:07:16,720
Get your family affairs

164
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:17,380
sorted out.

165
00:07:17,560 --> 00:07:18,510
I'll withdraw my investment!

166
00:07:18,510 --> 00:07:19,040
Move!

167
00:07:19,510 --> 00:07:20,570
I'm sorry. This...

168
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:21,800
You must stay!

169
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:23,070
How dare you leave?

170
00:07:23,070 --> 00:07:23,720
Come back here!

171
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:24,480
This is enough.

172
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:24,800
Stop yelling!

173
00:07:24,800 --> 00:07:26,600
You have no conscience, Chen Xiliang!

174
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:27,000
You...

175
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:28,360
Enough is enough!

176
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:29,040
Are you done with the fuss?

177
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:29,430
No!

178
00:07:29,510 --> 00:07:30,310
If Luna fails,

179
00:07:30,430 --> 00:07:31,430
I'll go bankrupt.

180
00:07:31,680 --> 00:07:33,680
Let's see who you can ask for money then.

181
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:35,040
No more talking. Let's go.

182
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:35,750
We'll get a divorce

183
00:07:35,750 --> 00:07:37,000
in the Civil Affairs Bureau!

184
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:37,600
Divorce?

185
00:07:37,870 --> 00:07:39,000
A divorce it is then!

186
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:40,120
I'm telling you, Chen Xiliang,

187
00:07:40,120 --> 00:07:40,720
if you divorce me,

188
00:07:40,720 --> 00:07:42,120
I won't let you take a single dime away!

189
00:07:42,120 --> 00:07:43,040
I won't take even a dime!

190
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:44,190
You can keep all the money at home.

191
00:07:44,190 --> 00:07:45,650
All I want is my brand Luna!

192
00:07:49,600 --> 00:07:52,560
[Clothing Tycoon Brutally Killed by
His Treacherous Young Wife]

193
00:07:51,630 --> 00:07:52,040
Wait.

194
00:07:52,920 --> 00:07:55,159
Chen Xiliang's treacherous second wife

195
00:07:55,159 --> 00:07:56,490
used to be his mistress.

196
00:07:56,950 --> 00:07:57,870
Could it be...

197
00:07:58,600 --> 00:07:59,630
that I've become

198
00:07:59,630 --> 00:08:01,030
Chen Xiliang's mistress

199
00:08:01,870 --> 00:08:03,120
in this world?

200
00:08:04,130 --> 00:08:05,360
This is ridiculous.

201
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:12,240
We're not able to establish

202
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:13,360
a materials center yet.

203
00:08:13,360 --> 00:08:14,800
For now, let's stay grounded

204
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:16,190
and focus on our small shop.

205
00:08:16,190 --> 00:08:17,070
Wei and I have

206
00:08:17,070 --> 00:08:18,160
learned our lesson.

207
00:08:18,160 --> 00:08:20,190
We won't overestimate ourselves again.

208
00:08:20,190 --> 00:08:21,650
Xiaolan, don't you worry.

209
00:08:22,190 --> 00:08:23,600
Kang Wei is really down-to-earth now.

210
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:24,660
I won't be worried.

211
00:08:27,830 --> 00:08:28,430
Xiaolan,

212
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:30,070
Cheng will be back next week.

213
00:08:30,070 --> 00:08:31,000
Just be patient.

214
00:08:33,720 --> 00:08:34,179
Coming!

215
00:08:36,750 --> 00:08:37,480
You're here.

216
00:08:38,320 --> 00:08:39,360
Hurry, come on in.

217
00:08:40,690 --> 00:08:41,419
I've told you

218
00:08:41,440 --> 00:08:42,750
not to bring anything over,

219
00:08:42,750 --> 00:08:44,080
since this is your home.

220
00:08:44,630 --> 00:08:45,090
Come on.

221
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:46,030
Take a seat.

222
00:08:46,240 --> 00:08:46,720
Wei.

223
00:08:48,150 --> 00:08:49,350
I own this apartment,

224
00:08:49,750 --> 00:08:50,880
but it's not my home.

225
00:08:52,670 --> 00:08:53,870
Actually, I came here

226
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:55,740
to tell you something.

227
00:09:04,240 --> 00:09:05,240
I need some more time

228
00:09:05,240 --> 00:09:06,700
to consider what you said.

229
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:21,550
Guo.

230
00:09:21,630 --> 00:09:22,230
Granny Yu.

231
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:23,910
Any mails for me?

232
00:09:24,030 --> 00:09:25,150
Or a package?

233
00:09:25,390 --> 00:09:25,990
Granny Yu,

234
00:09:26,160 --> 00:09:26,910
there hasn't been a mail

235
00:09:26,910 --> 00:09:29,110
or a package for you
during the New Year.

236
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:31,320
Could they have been missed?

237
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:32,850
Check carefully, will you?

238
00:09:32,910 --> 00:09:34,670
Granny Yu, we've checked several times.

239
00:09:34,670 --> 00:09:35,670
Nothing could've been missed.

240
00:09:35,670 --> 00:09:36,390
If there were anything for you,

241
00:09:36,390 --> 00:09:38,790
we would've delivered it
to your house already.

242
00:09:38,790 --> 00:09:40,030
I'm leaving then, Granny Yu.

243
00:09:40,030 --> 00:09:41,490
Please let me get through.

244
00:09:41,630 --> 00:09:42,390
Thanks.

245
00:09:42,410 --> 00:09:43,070
No problem.

246
00:09:57,240 --> 00:09:57,840
Xiaolan.

247
00:09:58,870 --> 00:09:59,480
Xiaolan?

248
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:02,750
You seem distracted. How come?

249
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:06,300
Are you fighting with Zhou Cheng?

250
00:10:07,440 --> 00:10:09,240
I'm not fighting with Zhou Cheng,

251
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:10,670
but myself.

252
00:10:11,840 --> 00:10:13,440
So many accidents have happened recently.

253
00:10:13,440 --> 00:10:14,770
I can't help but suspect

254
00:10:15,080 --> 00:10:16,610
if my appearance in this era

255
00:10:16,630 --> 00:10:18,890
has changed the fates of those around me.

256
00:10:19,030 --> 00:10:20,120
No.

257
00:10:20,390 --> 00:10:22,450
I'm not fighting with him, Granny Yu.

258
00:10:25,150 --> 00:10:25,870
Granny Yu,

259
00:10:26,630 --> 00:10:28,030
you've seen many things.

260
00:10:28,150 --> 00:10:29,150
I have a question.

261
00:10:29,680 --> 00:10:31,120
Do you think a person's fate

262
00:10:31,120 --> 00:10:32,180
is predetermined?

263
00:10:33,630 --> 00:10:35,000
Young people like you

264
00:10:35,200 --> 00:10:37,030
always think about stuff

265
00:10:37,390 --> 00:10:39,080
like fate and destiny.

266
00:10:40,360 --> 00:10:42,000
Dear, none of that means anything.

267
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:43,480
The thought of it is futile.

268
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:45,840
Living every day to its fullest

269
00:10:46,150 --> 00:10:47,750
matters more than anything.

270
00:10:49,600 --> 00:10:50,960
Aren't you worried that your decisions

271
00:10:50,960 --> 00:10:52,890
might change someone else's fate?

272
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:54,680
Do you have no regrets at all?

273
00:10:55,120 --> 00:10:55,750
What if you had

274
00:10:55,750 --> 00:10:58,350
refused to go to Nanyang
with others years ago?

275
00:11:01,690 --> 00:11:03,820
Sorry. I shouldn't have brought it up.

276
00:11:06,030 --> 00:11:07,690
It's fine. That's not a taboo.

277
00:11:08,730 --> 00:11:10,190
I've thought about it too.

278
00:11:11,790 --> 00:11:12,670
If...

279
00:11:13,480 --> 00:11:15,480
I could do it all over again,

280
00:11:16,510 --> 00:11:17,270
I'm not sure

281
00:11:17,270 --> 00:11:18,910
what decision I would make.

282
00:11:19,910 --> 00:11:22,000
Suppose I made the same decision,

283
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:24,120
it wouldn't necessarily lead to

284
00:11:24,120 --> 00:11:25,390
the same result.

285
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:26,970
Everyone...

286
00:11:27,580 --> 00:11:29,670
is pushed forward by time.

287
00:11:30,720 --> 00:11:31,720
Living a life

288
00:11:32,080 --> 00:11:33,480
is like dreaming a dream.

289
00:11:34,120 --> 00:11:35,780
Don't be too full of yourself.

290
00:11:36,030 --> 00:11:37,870
Does anyone really have the power

291
00:11:37,870 --> 00:11:39,600
to change someone else's fate?

292
00:11:53,610 --> 00:11:55,120
[Divorce Certificate]

293
00:11:57,320 --> 00:11:57,720
Xia,

294
00:11:59,150 --> 00:12:00,750
I've sorted everything out.

295
00:12:00,750 --> 00:12:01,720
I left all the cash at home

296
00:12:01,720 --> 00:12:02,720
with Lin Meijuan.

297
00:12:03,240 --> 00:12:04,720
Now, Luna is all I have.

298
00:12:05,270 --> 00:12:07,400
Can you not withdraw your investment?

299
00:12:09,630 --> 00:12:10,290
This is bad.

300
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:12,510
I have really become Chen's "mistress"

301
00:12:12,510 --> 00:12:13,970
in the original timeline.

302
00:12:14,630 --> 00:12:15,360
However,

303
00:12:15,670 --> 00:12:17,120
if I were her,

304
00:12:17,390 --> 00:12:19,450
there's no way I'd harm Chen Xiliang.

305
00:12:19,720 --> 00:12:21,030
So, in this timeline,

306
00:12:21,030 --> 00:12:22,030
Chen Xiliang will

307
00:12:22,080 --> 00:12:24,080
still become the future clothing tycoon.

308
00:12:24,080 --> 00:12:25,120
But he might not

309
00:12:25,120 --> 00:12:26,250
end up being killed.

310
00:12:26,840 --> 00:12:27,970
Granny Yu was right.

311
00:12:28,270 --> 00:12:29,870
Perhaps I'm just too full of myself.

312
00:12:29,870 --> 00:12:31,120
There is a chance

313
00:12:31,600 --> 00:12:32,470
that the recent happenings

314
00:12:32,470 --> 00:12:34,330
weren't caused by my appearance.

315
00:12:35,270 --> 00:12:35,720
Xia,

316
00:12:36,750 --> 00:12:38,010
please say something.

317
00:12:38,270 --> 00:12:39,270
Are you still mad?

318
00:12:39,480 --> 00:12:40,630
How can I not?

319
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:41,600
I told you to sort out

320
00:12:41,600 --> 00:12:43,120
things between you and your wife.

321
00:12:43,120 --> 00:12:44,320
Is this how you did it?

322
00:12:45,630 --> 00:12:47,840
A husband and wife may not
always be on the same boat

323
00:12:47,840 --> 00:12:48,970
or strive together,

324
00:12:49,360 --> 00:12:51,790
but they shouldn't hold each other back
at least.

325
00:12:51,790 --> 00:12:52,390
Chen,

326
00:12:52,840 --> 00:12:54,970
I think you were right to get a divorce.

327
00:13:00,390 --> 00:13:02,080
Have all the assets been divided?

328
00:13:02,080 --> 00:13:03,440
I'd hate for Luna to be dragged

329
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:04,240
into some sort

330
00:13:04,240 --> 00:13:06,100
of divorce dispute in the future.

331
00:13:06,550 --> 00:13:07,550
It's all settled.

332
00:13:07,630 --> 00:13:08,160
I just...

333
00:13:09,390 --> 00:13:10,720
Does this mean you won't

334
00:13:11,000 --> 00:13:12,530
withdraw your investment?

335
00:13:14,030 --> 00:13:15,690
I'll take your silence as yes.

336
00:13:17,550 --> 00:13:18,750
Chen Xiliang,

337
00:13:18,870 --> 00:13:20,440
how come I never noticed before

338
00:13:20,440 --> 00:13:21,770
that you're so cunning?

339
00:13:22,240 --> 00:13:24,110
You've even got Granny Yu on your side.

340
00:13:24,110 --> 00:13:25,550
It's not like I used devious means.

341
00:13:25,550 --> 00:13:26,240
I just...

342
00:13:26,240 --> 00:13:27,720
had to do what I had to do.

343
00:13:33,440 --> 00:13:34,570
My phone's ringing.

344
00:13:36,870 --> 00:13:37,270
Hello?

345
00:13:37,900 --> 00:13:38,630
Mr. Cui.

346
00:13:40,240 --> 00:13:42,570
The issue
for the second half of the month?

347
00:13:43,220 --> 00:13:44,150
No problem.

348
00:13:44,150 --> 00:13:44,630
Okay.

349
00:13:44,910 --> 00:13:45,550
Thanks.

350
00:13:46,120 --> 00:13:47,200
Thank you so much.

351
00:13:47,390 --> 00:13:47,790
Bye.

352
00:13:49,360 --> 00:13:51,080
You were just whining to me
about being poor.

353
00:13:51,080 --> 00:13:52,360
But now you're using
a brick phone already.

354
00:13:52,360 --> 00:13:53,360
Stop teasing me.

355
00:13:53,550 --> 00:13:54,080
I just...

356
00:13:54,550 --> 00:13:57,080
need it to b-bring in projects.
Can't you see?

357
00:13:57,630 --> 00:13:58,670
Honestly, there isn't

358
00:13:58,670 --> 00:14:00,270
much money left in my pocket.

359
00:14:00,480 --> 00:14:01,200
Besides,

360
00:14:01,280 --> 00:14:02,760
Luna is a mid-range brand.

361
00:14:02,790 --> 00:14:04,650
We have to boost its image, right?

362
00:14:04,670 --> 00:14:06,320
That call was from Mr. Cui.

363
00:14:06,600 --> 00:14:08,320
He said Wu Kaili's photos
from the Chinese New Year Gala

364
00:14:08,320 --> 00:14:11,050
could get on
the second half of the month's issue.

365
00:14:11,600 --> 00:14:13,400
About what you told me last time,

366
00:14:13,670 --> 00:14:15,800
t-that "native advertising" thingy,

367
00:14:16,070 --> 00:14:17,400
how do we approach that?

368
00:14:19,120 --> 00:14:20,150
Native advertising

369
00:14:20,150 --> 00:14:22,720
means hiding advertisements

370
00:14:22,720 --> 00:14:24,580
in seemingly ordinary articles.

371
00:14:24,750 --> 00:14:26,720
For instance, we can write a piece

372
00:14:27,240 --> 00:14:28,360
in an editor's tone,

373
00:14:28,360 --> 00:14:29,200
saying that one day,

374
00:14:29,200 --> 00:14:30,440
he or she went across a shop

375
00:14:30,440 --> 00:14:31,720
and discovered the items for sale

376
00:14:31,720 --> 00:14:33,850
were from a domestic brand named Luna.

377
00:14:33,870 --> 00:14:35,600
He or she then took a look inside

378
00:14:36,100 --> 00:14:37,440
and found that Luna was the brand

379
00:14:37,440 --> 00:14:39,870
that Wu Kaili wore to
the Chinese New Year Gala.

380
00:14:39,870 --> 00:14:40,790
Readers nowadays

381
00:14:40,790 --> 00:14:42,200
haven't gotten very alert

382
00:14:42,200 --> 00:14:43,280
about such content,

383
00:14:43,280 --> 00:14:44,360
so they could easily be tricked

384
00:14:44,360 --> 00:14:45,550
by cunning businessmen like you

385
00:14:45,550 --> 00:14:46,680
without knowing it.

386
00:14:46,720 --> 00:14:48,780
H-How am I a cunning businessman now?

387
00:14:49,440 --> 00:14:50,550
But this idea of yours

388
00:14:50,550 --> 00:14:51,270
is brilliant.

389
00:14:51,270 --> 00:14:53,000
I would never come up with that.

390
00:14:53,320 --> 00:14:54,720
In the era I'm from,

391
00:14:54,960 --> 00:14:56,030
this is common practice.

392
00:14:56,030 --> 00:14:56,630
Tell me more

393
00:14:56,630 --> 00:14:57,160
about it.

394
00:14:57,200 --> 00:14:57,790
You just gave

395
00:14:57,790 --> 00:14:58,840
a few lines. Tell me more

396
00:14:58,840 --> 00:14:59,320
of that stuff.

397
00:14:59,320 --> 00:15:00,520
I-I'll write it down.

398
00:15:02,470 --> 00:15:04,380
[Fashion Guide]

399
00:15:05,080 --> 00:15:05,880
Okay. Thanks.

400
00:15:08,510 --> 00:15:10,080
Clothes by Luna?

401
00:15:10,270 --> 00:15:11,720
Even that Gangdao celebrity Wu Kaili

402
00:15:11,720 --> 00:15:12,630
wears this brand.

403
00:15:12,630 --> 00:15:13,480
So beautiful!

404
00:15:13,630 --> 00:15:14,690
I love this outfit.

405
00:15:14,870 --> 00:15:15,360
Look,

406
00:15:15,750 --> 00:15:16,630
clothes by Luna.

407
00:15:16,510 --> 00:15:21,820
[Luna]

408
00:15:23,320 --> 00:15:24,510
Look, that's Wu Kaili!

409
00:15:24,510 --> 00:15:25,670
Yeah. She's so pretty.

410
00:15:25,110 --> 00:15:26,390
[The same brand wore by Gangdao celebrity
Wu Kaili in the Chinese New Year Gala]

411
00:15:41,840 --> 00:15:43,080
Class act by Mr. Cui.

412
00:15:43,600 --> 00:15:44,480
Next, we'll be racing

413
00:15:44,480 --> 00:15:45,360
against time.

414
00:15:45,840 --> 00:15:46,750
After this issue hits the stands,

415
00:15:46,750 --> 00:15:48,550
there will be about a ten-day buzz.

416
00:15:48,550 --> 00:15:49,270
We must open the store

417
00:15:49,270 --> 00:15:50,800
within this period of time.

418
00:15:51,200 --> 00:15:52,860
What should be the exact date?

419
00:15:55,320 --> 00:15:56,180
February 20th,

420
00:15:56,440 --> 00:15:57,700
the Lantern Festival.

421
00:15:58,000 --> 00:15:58,730
Good choice.

422
00:16:03,510 --> 00:16:03,910
Hello?

423
00:16:04,270 --> 00:16:04,910
Cheng.

424
00:16:05,750 --> 00:16:07,480
Are you done with your business yet?

425
00:16:07,480 --> 00:16:08,600
The Luna store is going to open.

426
00:16:08,600 --> 00:16:09,550
You have to be back soon,

427
00:16:09,550 --> 00:16:10,630
or you'll miss the opening.

428
00:16:10,630 --> 00:16:12,670
What kind of supportive boyfriend are you?

429
00:16:12,670 --> 00:16:13,510
Cut it out.

430
00:16:14,440 --> 00:16:15,510
I'm almost done here.

431
00:16:15,510 --> 00:16:16,640
I'll be back in time.

432
00:16:17,150 --> 00:16:17,750
Well...

433
00:16:18,550 --> 00:16:19,750
How has Xiaolan been?

434
00:16:20,150 --> 00:16:22,010
You're asking me how she's doing?

435
00:16:22,910 --> 00:16:24,240
Aren't you two in touch?

436
00:16:25,390 --> 00:16:26,440
I've tried calling

437
00:16:26,440 --> 00:16:27,500
Granny Yu's place.

438
00:16:27,750 --> 00:16:29,350
Yet Xiaolan is never around.

439
00:16:29,840 --> 00:16:31,550
Xiaolan is just too busy

440
00:16:31,670 --> 00:16:32,670
to talk to you.

441
00:16:33,360 --> 00:16:33,890
Alright.

442
00:16:34,730 --> 00:16:35,720
Anyway, if anything comes up,

443
00:16:35,720 --> 00:16:36,550
try helping out

444
00:16:36,550 --> 00:16:37,410
more actively.

445
00:16:38,200 --> 00:16:39,060
I'm hanging up.

446
00:16:44,440 --> 00:16:44,970
Xiaolan,

447
00:16:45,910 --> 00:16:47,640
are you really just being busy?

448
00:16:56,390 --> 00:16:56,910
This

449
00:16:57,200 --> 00:16:59,400
is Ms. Xia, who I told you about earlier.

450
00:16:59,750 --> 00:17:00,680
In the next week,

451
00:17:00,840 --> 00:17:01,870
you'll receive

452
00:17:02,030 --> 00:17:03,690
pre-job training right here.

453
00:17:03,790 --> 00:17:05,000
So that's Ms. Xia?

454
00:17:05,440 --> 00:17:06,920
She looks even younger than me.

455
00:17:06,920 --> 00:17:07,790
Watch your tongue.

456
00:17:07,790 --> 00:17:08,990
Observe discipline.

457
00:17:09,940 --> 00:17:10,829
Hello, everyone.

458
00:17:10,829 --> 00:17:11,960
I am Xia Xiaolan,

459
00:17:12,310 --> 00:17:14,160
also a co-owner of Luna.

460
00:17:14,510 --> 00:17:15,480
Luna is positioned

461
00:17:15,480 --> 00:17:16,550
as mid-range women's wear.

462
00:17:16,550 --> 00:17:18,240
We strive for a competitive edge
in service,

463
00:17:18,240 --> 00:17:19,700
style, and brand effects.

464
00:17:19,750 --> 00:17:20,750
Your image exactly

465
00:17:20,750 --> 00:17:22,480
represents the brand's image.

466
00:17:23,000 --> 00:17:25,349
You will be trained in areas
of etiquette, styling,

467
00:17:25,349 --> 00:17:26,430
sales scripts,

468
00:17:26,589 --> 00:17:28,119
and marketing strategies.

469
00:17:29,200 --> 00:17:29,960
Now, please

470
00:17:30,270 --> 00:17:31,130
meet Granny Yu,

471
00:17:31,550 --> 00:17:33,150
your etiquette instructor.

472
00:17:35,400 --> 00:17:35,930
Alright.

473
00:17:36,750 --> 00:17:39,070
I'd like to lay some ground rules now.

474
00:17:39,480 --> 00:17:41,400
Training involves hardships.

475
00:17:42,200 --> 00:17:44,060
Have all of you had breakfast yet?

476
00:17:44,590 --> 00:17:45,310
-Yes.
-Yes.

477
00:17:46,270 --> 00:17:46,680
Good.

478
00:17:48,070 --> 00:17:50,830
Now, please stand against the wall.

479
00:17:53,750 --> 00:17:54,810
Did you not hear me?

480
00:17:55,400 --> 00:17:56,030
Go!

481
00:17:56,280 --> 00:17:56,690
Hurry.

482
00:17:56,720 --> 00:17:57,850
Class has begun. Go!

483
00:18:03,440 --> 00:18:05,440
Pretty looks are wasted

484
00:18:05,750 --> 00:18:07,830
without an upright posture,

485
00:18:08,160 --> 00:18:10,420
for elegance is what gives them meaning.

486
00:18:10,960 --> 00:18:11,790
Stand against the wall.

487
00:18:11,790 --> 00:18:13,590
Shoulders against the wall too.

488
00:18:13,590 --> 00:18:14,650
Your heels as well.

489
00:18:14,750 --> 00:18:16,720
Every part mentioned must touch the wall.

490
00:18:16,720 --> 00:18:17,790
Straighten your back.

491
00:18:17,790 --> 00:18:19,050
Today's class is about

492
00:18:19,200 --> 00:18:20,800
how to put on a perfect smile.

493
00:18:21,000 --> 00:18:22,530
Everyone can smile, right?

494
00:18:22,750 --> 00:18:23,510
The point is,

495
00:18:23,720 --> 00:18:24,960
how to smile cutely

496
00:18:25,240 --> 00:18:26,550
and beautifully.

497
00:18:27,070 --> 00:18:28,200
Seeing such lovely smiles,

498
00:18:28,200 --> 00:18:29,060
customers will

499
00:18:29,240 --> 00:18:30,920
feel welcome when they get in the store

500
00:18:30,920 --> 00:18:33,110
and have the desire to buy our clothes.

501
00:18:33,510 --> 00:18:34,550
So, today,

502
00:18:34,680 --> 00:18:36,340
you'll practice how to smile.

503
00:18:39,590 --> 00:18:42,160
I'm having you walk in place
with books on your heads

504
00:18:42,160 --> 00:18:44,960
so you can learn
how to keep your posture straight.

505
00:18:45,680 --> 00:18:46,940
Lift your legs higher.

506
00:18:47,720 --> 00:18:48,790
Goodbye, Granny Yu.

507
00:18:48,790 --> 00:18:49,270
Bye.

508
00:18:52,650 --> 00:18:53,310
These 7 points

509
00:18:53,310 --> 00:18:54,720
conclude

510
00:18:54,720 --> 00:18:56,510
the clothing sales skills

511
00:18:56,510 --> 00:18:57,510
I just mentioned.

512
00:18:57,590 --> 00:18:58,920
What makes a good outfit

513
00:18:59,110 --> 00:19:00,200
is the styling.

514
00:19:00,440 --> 00:19:01,770
Now, let's give it a try.

515
00:19:02,240 --> 00:19:03,840
You Li, please come forward.

516
00:19:03,930 --> 00:19:05,920
Remember the way she looks and feels

517
00:19:05,920 --> 00:19:06,880
in this dress.

518
00:19:07,000 --> 00:19:08,730
Twenty-two, twenty-three...

519
00:19:10,880 --> 00:19:11,480
Very good.

520
00:19:12,880 --> 00:19:13,480
Very good.

521
00:19:15,110 --> 00:19:15,570
Come on.

522
00:19:17,270 --> 00:19:17,750
So pretty.

523
00:19:17,750 --> 00:19:19,750
This is the charm of styling.

524
00:19:21,350 --> 00:19:22,680
Granny Yu, here we come.

525
00:19:22,680 --> 00:19:23,940
Granny Yu, we're here.

526
00:19:41,550 --> 00:19:43,750
Greetings, Ms. Xia, Ms. Liu.

527
00:19:43,830 --> 00:19:46,070
Welcome to Luna Womenswear.

528
00:19:48,830 --> 00:19:50,160
How wonderful.

529
00:19:50,480 --> 00:19:52,270
Granny Yu, you are amazing.

530
00:19:52,720 --> 00:19:53,680
How did you train them

531
00:19:53,680 --> 00:19:54,830
to be so professional?

532
00:19:54,830 --> 00:19:55,760
Perfect, right?

533
00:19:57,600 --> 00:19:58,720
Before the opening,

534
00:19:58,720 --> 00:19:59,790
there is an extra assignment

535
00:19:59,790 --> 00:20:00,750
for you all.

536
00:20:01,160 --> 00:20:02,480
Shengcheng is a port city

537
00:20:02,480 --> 00:20:03,620
adjacent to Gangdao.

538
00:20:03,620 --> 00:20:04,650
Many of our customers

539
00:20:04,650 --> 00:20:06,160
will be from overseas

540
00:20:06,180 --> 00:20:06,980
or Gangdao.

541
00:20:07,440 --> 00:20:08,880
So, in your spare time,

542
00:20:08,880 --> 00:20:10,400
try learning Cantonese

543
00:20:10,400 --> 00:20:11,200
and English.

544
00:20:11,440 --> 00:20:12,790
After all, one more language you speak

545
00:20:12,790 --> 00:20:14,760
means one more potential customer.

546
00:20:14,760 --> 00:20:15,440
You know that

547
00:20:15,440 --> 00:20:17,300
without me explaining it, right?

548
00:20:17,310 --> 00:20:18,240
Now, I announce,

549
00:20:18,310 --> 00:20:19,440
you've all successfully

550
00:20:19,440 --> 00:20:20,840
completed the training!

551
00:20:25,000 --> 00:20:25,960
I wish you

552
00:20:26,160 --> 00:20:28,720
a grand opening and a booming business!

553
00:20:32,430 --> 00:20:33,000
Bye.

554
00:20:33,030 --> 00:20:34,690
-Bye.
-You girls are the best!

555
00:20:35,000 --> 00:20:36,200
Get home safe.

556
00:20:36,550 --> 00:20:36,960
Sure!

557
00:20:36,960 --> 00:20:37,790
Don't be late tomorrow.

558
00:20:37,790 --> 00:20:38,240
Okay.

559
00:20:38,750 --> 00:20:39,750
Good work.

560
00:20:44,550 --> 00:20:46,480
It's been a long time since he left.

561
00:20:46,510 --> 00:20:48,370
Aren't you going to do something?

562
00:20:48,400 --> 00:20:50,200
Zhou Cheng told me he'd solve the problem.

563
00:20:50,200 --> 00:20:50,880
I trust him.

564
00:20:53,030 --> 00:20:54,490
Trust is all that matters.

565
00:20:56,920 --> 00:20:57,450
Let's go.

566
00:20:58,110 --> 00:20:59,040
Ms. Xia, Ms. Xia!

567
00:20:59,400 --> 00:21:00,200
Wait a moment.

568
00:21:00,550 --> 00:21:01,510
What is it, You?

569
00:21:02,200 --> 00:21:02,790
Ms. Xia,

570
00:21:03,000 --> 00:21:03,790
I was too embarrassed to say this

571
00:21:03,790 --> 00:21:05,350
with that many people around just now.

572
00:21:05,350 --> 00:21:06,810
I'd love to learn English.

573
00:21:06,930 --> 00:21:07,790
But I have no idea

574
00:21:07,790 --> 00:21:09,110
where to start,

575
00:21:09,550 --> 00:21:11,880
since I dropped out from middle school...

576
00:21:12,440 --> 00:21:13,240
That's okay.

577
00:21:13,730 --> 00:21:15,560
If you're completely new at it,

578
00:21:15,590 --> 00:21:17,120
just start with listening.

579
00:21:17,350 --> 00:21:18,920
Forget about reading and writing.

580
00:21:18,920 --> 00:21:20,550
First, try to memorize the sentences

581
00:21:20,550 --> 00:21:21,510
and phrases

582
00:21:21,510 --> 00:21:23,530
that are often used in life or at work.

583
00:21:23,530 --> 00:21:24,640
Tell you what, come with me.

584
00:21:24,640 --> 00:21:25,970
I'll get you some books.

585
00:21:26,440 --> 00:21:27,350
Thank you, Ms. Xia.

586
00:21:27,350 --> 00:21:27,750
Here.

587
00:21:28,270 --> 00:21:29,590
Tomorrow, both stores in Shengcheng

588
00:21:29,590 --> 00:21:31,160
and Longcheng will open at the same time.

589
00:21:31,160 --> 00:21:33,110
I'm sure everything will go smoothly.

590
00:21:33,110 --> 00:21:33,790
Chen,

591
00:21:33,960 --> 00:21:35,160
don't be too nervous.

592
00:21:35,160 --> 00:21:36,560
Get a good night's sleep.

593
00:21:36,830 --> 00:21:38,630
May the openings be successful.

594
00:21:46,030 --> 00:21:46,690
Zhou Cheng,

595
00:21:47,550 --> 00:21:48,640
I've sorted out

596
00:21:48,640 --> 00:21:49,680
my feelings.

597
00:21:51,000 --> 00:21:52,860
Have you solved your problem yet?

598
00:21:54,000 --> 00:21:55,000
I miss you so much.

599
00:22:01,970 --> 00:22:07,930
♪ Watching the flowers fall,
lonely I ask the night sky ♪

600
00:22:08,590 --> 00:22:13,810
♪ Is spring hazy where you are? ♪

601
00:22:15,660 --> 00:22:20,470
♪ Time is upside down,
the seasons intertwine ♪

602
00:22:21,210 --> 00:22:27,320
♪ Fate seems to want us to stay silent ♪

603
00:22:28,770 --> 00:22:31,720
♪ Time is so stingy ♪

604
00:22:31,740 --> 00:22:35,080
♪ It takes away even the memories ♪

605
00:22:35,980 --> 00:22:38,580
♪ But I still remember ♪

606
00:22:38,770 --> 00:22:43,060
♪ The promises of love ♪

607
00:22:43,260 --> 00:22:45,720
♪ Call out to me with all your strength ♪

608
00:22:45,740 --> 00:22:50,450
♪ Let the whole starry sky sparkle ♪

609
00:22:49,880 --> 00:22:50,410
Xiaolan.

610
00:22:50,470 --> 00:22:53,040
♪ Respond to me with all your heart ♪

611
00:22:52,000 --> 00:22:53,030
This has been

612
00:22:53,060 --> 00:22:57,610
♪ Across the ends of the earth,
we won't stop ♪

613
00:22:54,110 --> 00:22:55,170
a really long week.

614
00:22:58,090 --> 00:23:01,860
♪ No matter how fierce the storms,
I won't back down ♪

615
00:23:01,880 --> 00:23:06,080
♪ I'll run toward the harbor
where you are ♪

616
00:23:02,030 --> 00:23:02,890
I have properly

617
00:23:03,110 --> 00:23:04,240
handled the matter.

618
00:23:06,310 --> 00:23:07,070
Previously,

619
00:23:06,990 --> 00:23:11,560
♪ Together, forever ♪

620
00:23:07,920 --> 00:23:09,000
I didn't realize

621
00:23:09,590 --> 00:23:10,400
Shi Kai's family

622
00:23:10,400 --> 00:23:11,730
didn't need pity or help

623
00:23:12,350 --> 00:23:13,680
beyond all boundaries.

624
00:23:14,720 --> 00:23:16,650
They should stand on their own feet

625
00:23:16,920 --> 00:23:18,050
and face the future.

626
00:23:19,160 --> 00:23:20,360
I should also stand up

627
00:23:21,440 --> 00:23:22,640
and go on with my life—

628
00:23:28,920 --> 00:23:30,180
a life shared with you.

629
00:23:36,430 --> 00:23:39,550
[Passbook for Current Deposits]

630
00:23:40,160 --> 00:23:41,270
It contains the money

631
00:23:41,270 --> 00:23:42,110
I earned from the business

632
00:23:42,110 --> 00:23:43,510
I did with Wei in the past,

633
00:23:43,790 --> 00:23:45,790
along with my salary for over a year,

634
00:23:46,030 --> 00:23:46,590
bonuses,

635
00:23:47,400 --> 00:23:48,510
and even the lucky money I received

636
00:23:48,510 --> 00:23:49,310
in childhood.

637
00:23:49,680 --> 00:23:50,310
Anyway,

638
00:23:50,720 --> 00:23:51,920
every penny to my name

639
00:23:52,440 --> 00:23:53,500
is in this account.

640
00:23:54,510 --> 00:23:56,000
I'd love for you to have it all.

641
00:23:56,000 --> 00:23:57,110
What are you doing?

642
00:23:57,720 --> 00:23:59,880
Throwing money at me instead of making

643
00:24:00,400 --> 00:24:01,530
romantic gestures?

644
00:24:04,110 --> 00:24:05,440
I know you don't care for
my little savings,

645
00:24:05,440 --> 00:24:06,900
now that you're a big boss.

646
00:24:08,590 --> 00:24:10,350
You're pretty rich, counselor.

647
00:24:10,350 --> 00:24:11,550
There's over 60,000.

648
00:24:12,000 --> 00:24:12,790
Alright then.

649
00:24:12,790 --> 00:24:14,240
I'll keep it safe for you.

650
00:24:17,440 --> 00:24:18,100
Zhou Cheng.

651
00:24:19,830 --> 00:24:21,240
Actually, I also owe you

652
00:24:21,240 --> 00:24:21,900
an apology.

653
00:24:23,210 --> 00:24:25,520
These days, with Luna stores' openings

654
00:24:25,550 --> 00:24:26,920
and many other affairs,

655
00:24:27,200 --> 00:24:28,270
I became so busy

656
00:24:28,590 --> 00:24:29,790
that I neglected you.

657
00:24:31,240 --> 00:24:33,270
To show how sorry I am,

658
00:24:33,720 --> 00:24:34,830
should I also hand over

659
00:24:34,830 --> 00:24:36,090
my passbook to you too?

660
00:24:38,510 --> 00:24:39,640
I wouldn't dare take

661
00:24:39,640 --> 00:24:41,170
such huge advantage of you.

662
00:24:41,920 --> 00:24:42,450
Xiaolan.

663
00:24:44,310 --> 00:24:45,000
I know...

664
00:24:46,200 --> 00:24:47,000
you've been through

665
00:24:47,000 --> 00:24:47,830
a lot lately.

666
00:24:49,790 --> 00:24:51,850
I should've spent more time with you.

667
00:24:52,400 --> 00:24:53,060
I assure you

668
00:24:53,680 --> 00:24:54,550
that from now on,

669
00:24:54,550 --> 00:24:55,510
I'll definitely be

670
00:24:55,510 --> 00:24:57,170
a more supportive boyfriend.

671
00:24:57,720 --> 00:24:58,780
When you're tired,

672
00:24:59,240 --> 00:25:00,700
just lean on my shoulders.

673
00:25:02,350 --> 00:25:03,680
I'm very tired now.

674
00:25:04,510 --> 00:25:06,510
Then lean on my shoulders, will you?

675
00:25:26,110 --> 00:25:28,630
[Warm Congratulations on
the Grand Opening of Luna Clothing Store]

676
00:26:10,750 --> 00:26:11,160
Bravo!

677
00:26:11,400 --> 00:26:12,590
Bravo!

678
00:26:14,240 --> 00:26:15,590
Luna Clothing Store...

679
00:26:16,000 --> 00:26:18,440
is officially open!

680
00:26:21,700 --> 00:26:23,640
For our grand opening,
12% is off on all items!

681
00:26:23,640 --> 00:26:25,450
Please come in and have a look!

682
00:26:25,480 --> 00:26:25,880
Bravo!

683
00:26:25,880 --> 00:26:27,000
Welcome!

684
00:26:28,830 --> 00:26:30,680
Welcome! Welcome!

685
00:26:30,700 --> 00:26:32,300
Watch your step. Be careful.

686
00:26:32,310 --> 00:26:32,920
Welcome!

687
00:26:32,960 --> 00:26:33,620
Be careful.

688
00:26:38,110 --> 00:26:39,200
Here's the checkout counter.

689
00:26:39,200 --> 00:26:40,730
Everything is discounted.

690
00:26:41,000 --> 00:26:41,460
Please,

691
00:26:41,550 --> 00:26:42,110
this way.

692
00:26:42,240 --> 00:26:42,680
Hello.

693
00:26:43,070 --> 00:26:43,720
Follow me.

694
00:26:43,720 --> 00:26:44,270
Let's go!

695
00:26:44,550 --> 00:26:45,080
Let's go.

696
00:26:46,070 --> 00:26:46,590
Here!

697
00:26:47,510 --> 00:26:48,240
Here, here.

698
00:26:49,440 --> 00:26:49,920
Sis Bai,

699
00:26:50,400 --> 00:26:51,200
foreign customers, huh?

700
00:26:51,200 --> 00:26:51,930
I saw them.

701
00:26:52,320 --> 00:26:53,440
The lights are really

702
00:26:53,440 --> 00:26:54,640
making a difference.

703
00:26:54,640 --> 00:26:55,680
-Yes.
-Everything looks high-class.

704
00:26:55,680 --> 00:26:56,640
How prosperous.

705
00:26:58,040 --> 00:26:59,280
This is my first time

706
00:26:59,310 --> 00:27:00,640
seeing Auntie at work.

707
00:27:00,880 --> 00:27:02,480
Quite different from usual.

708
00:27:02,680 --> 00:27:03,550
When Auntie

709
00:27:03,550 --> 00:27:04,550
was in Jingcheng,

710
00:27:04,570 --> 00:27:06,770
she could already manage a store alone.

711
00:27:11,160 --> 00:27:12,960
What are you looking at? Go help.

712
00:27:12,960 --> 00:27:13,920
What can I help with?

713
00:27:13,920 --> 00:27:15,380
Every staffer is busy now.

714
00:27:16,920 --> 00:27:17,720
This is yours.

715
00:27:19,400 --> 00:27:20,250
-Welcome.
-Welcome.

716
00:27:20,250 --> 00:27:20,750
Come on in, please.

717
00:27:20,750 --> 00:27:22,640
A 12% discount on everything
for today's grand opening.

718
00:27:22,640 --> 00:27:23,700
Take a look inside.

719
00:27:23,720 --> 00:27:25,120
Welcome! Please come in!

720
00:27:34,640 --> 00:27:35,830
Mr. Du wishes Luna—

721
00:27:36,240 --> 00:27:39,030
a successful opening
and a booming business!

722
00:27:42,350 --> 00:27:43,550
What kind of stunt

723
00:27:43,840 --> 00:27:45,300
is Du Zhaohui pulling now?

724
00:27:45,640 --> 00:27:49,000
The flowers have arrived.
Why are these people still around?

725
00:27:49,000 --> 00:27:50,400
Fellas, thank you.

726
00:27:50,720 --> 00:27:51,790
Tell Mr. Du I say thank you

727
00:27:51,790 --> 00:27:52,640
when you get back.

728
00:27:52,640 --> 00:27:53,840
The flowers can stay.

729
00:27:53,920 --> 00:27:54,920
You may leave now.

730
00:27:55,000 --> 00:27:55,830
Got it, Ms. Xia.

731
00:27:55,830 --> 00:27:57,110
Thank you, Ms. Xia!

732
00:28:04,160 --> 00:28:04,760
Everyone,

733
00:28:05,350 --> 00:28:06,880
we're having something light today—

734
00:28:06,880 --> 00:28:08,790
goji berry soup with assorted mushroom.

735
00:28:08,790 --> 00:28:10,120
Come on, help yourself.

736
00:28:11,510 --> 00:28:13,710
I had this soup simmered for a long time.

737
00:28:14,030 --> 00:28:14,830
Young Master,

738
00:28:15,180 --> 00:28:16,450
the task in Shengcheng

739
00:28:16,920 --> 00:28:18,960
is complete. Flowers were sent,

740
00:28:19,120 --> 00:28:20,110
and everything else taken care of.

741
00:28:20,110 --> 00:28:22,750
The ribbon-cutting ceremony
is in the afternoon.

742
00:28:22,750 --> 00:28:23,720
I hate this stupid

743
00:28:23,720 --> 00:28:25,050
Spring Reception Party

744
00:28:25,350 --> 00:28:27,810
for holding me back
from the ribbon cutting.

745
00:28:27,920 --> 00:28:29,200
If only I could cut the ribbon

746
00:28:29,200 --> 00:28:30,330
with Xia Xiaolan...

747
00:28:33,440 --> 00:28:35,300
Young Master, care for some soup?

748
00:28:41,830 --> 00:28:43,490
A toast from Zhaoji to you all.

749
00:28:44,400 --> 00:28:46,260
Many thanks, uncles and aunties.

750
00:28:47,880 --> 00:28:49,410
Do look after my son, folks.

751
00:28:51,960 --> 00:28:53,270
I'm not eating anything. Go get the car.

752
00:28:53,270 --> 00:28:53,680
Yes.

753
00:28:57,830 --> 00:28:59,310
Alright. Be seated, please.

754
00:28:59,310 --> 00:28:59,640
Come.

755
00:29:01,310 --> 00:29:01,640
Hey!

756
00:29:01,830 --> 00:29:02,440
Everyone,

757
00:29:02,640 --> 00:29:03,960
enjoy the feast.

758
00:29:06,030 --> 00:29:06,830
Young Master!

759
00:29:10,440 --> 00:29:11,830
Have the Shengcheng police
taken action yet?

760
00:29:11,830 --> 00:29:13,070
Yes, they have.

761
00:29:13,830 --> 00:29:14,960
I hope my old man will like

762
00:29:14,960 --> 00:29:15,920
this spring celebration gift

763
00:29:15,920 --> 00:29:16,510
from me.

764
00:29:16,750 --> 00:29:17,610
He surely will.

765
00:29:17,750 --> 00:29:18,750
Xia Xiaolan has always wanted

766
00:29:18,750 --> 00:29:19,790
to see me do serious business, right?

767
00:29:19,790 --> 00:29:20,200
Right.

768
00:29:21,030 --> 00:29:22,310
I'll show her how I get it done this time.

769
00:29:22,310 --> 00:29:23,200
No problem.

770
00:29:23,350 --> 00:29:24,160
Let's go back to Shengcheng.

771
00:29:24,160 --> 00:29:24,510
Sure!

772
00:29:29,590 --> 00:29:30,390
Young Master,

773
00:29:30,440 --> 00:29:31,640
it's "Lady Plastic."

774
00:29:44,790 --> 00:29:46,880
Why stare at us? Plastic freak.

775
00:29:48,000 --> 00:29:48,790
Young Master,

776
00:29:48,790 --> 00:29:50,240
when we get to Shengcheng,

777
00:29:50,240 --> 00:29:50,920
shall we head straight

778
00:29:50,920 --> 00:29:52,400
to Ms. Xia's clothing store?

779
00:29:52,400 --> 00:29:54,270
Forget it. Let's go back to the hotel.

780
00:29:54,270 --> 00:29:55,310
Send a message to Ms. Xia.

781
00:29:55,310 --> 00:29:55,880
Tell her

782
00:29:56,270 --> 00:29:57,470
that I, Du Zhaohui, am

783
00:29:57,510 --> 00:29:58,920
going to do serious business.

784
00:29:58,920 --> 00:29:59,580
Sure thing.

785
00:30:00,550 --> 00:30:02,080
Impressive, Young Master.

786
00:30:08,310 --> 00:30:09,510
Take your time trying them on.

787
00:30:09,510 --> 00:30:10,840
There are many options.

788
00:30:11,030 --> 00:30:12,630
This color is also very good.

789
00:30:16,230 --> 00:30:17,890
Do you have another shoe size?

790
00:30:18,350 --> 00:30:18,880
This?

791
00:30:19,240 --> 00:30:20,310
Yes, this is cool.

792
00:30:20,970 --> 00:30:23,690
[Luna]

793
00:30:28,710 --> 00:30:33,000
[Closed]

794
00:30:58,890 --> 00:31:02,530
[Spring, 1990] [Panpan the Panda;
Embracing the Asian Games]

795
00:31:03,340 --> 00:31:04,890
[Closed]

796
00:31:09,000 --> 00:31:09,350
Four.

797
00:31:10,240 --> 00:31:13,640
Six, seven, eight, nine, ten, eleven,

798
00:31:13,830 --> 00:31:14,430
twelve...

799
00:31:14,720 --> 00:31:15,510
Ms. Xia, Ms. Liu,

800
00:31:15,510 --> 00:31:16,030
we've restocked

801
00:31:16,030 --> 00:31:17,000
the sold-out items.

802
00:31:17,000 --> 00:31:18,350
This is today's inventory list.

803
00:31:18,350 --> 00:31:19,240
Okay. Back to your work then.

804
00:31:19,240 --> 00:31:19,590
Yes.

805
00:31:24,640 --> 00:31:25,000
Mom,

806
00:31:25,680 --> 00:31:27,070
we can open branch stores now.

807
00:31:27,070 --> 00:31:27,640
Really?

808
00:31:32,690 --> 00:31:33,440
Being on the Chinese New Year Gala

809
00:31:33,440 --> 00:31:34,750
and in magazines
has really brought great publicity

810
00:31:34,750 --> 00:31:35,550
to our brand.

811
00:31:35,880 --> 00:31:37,240
The initial investments were huge.

812
00:31:37,240 --> 00:31:38,830
I can't believe we've made profits

813
00:31:38,830 --> 00:31:40,030
within just one year.

814
00:31:40,270 --> 00:31:41,480
Though the costs on factories,

815
00:31:41,480 --> 00:31:42,440
channels, and stores

816
00:31:42,440 --> 00:31:43,880
in the early stages were massive,

817
00:31:43,880 --> 00:31:45,690
at least we didn't have to pay
any middlemen.

818
00:31:45,690 --> 00:31:46,720
We'll benefit from this mode

819
00:31:46,720 --> 00:31:47,580
in the long run,

820
00:31:47,750 --> 00:31:49,280
as it not only reduces costs

821
00:31:49,440 --> 00:31:52,050
but also enables us
to control the brand's quality.

822
00:31:52,050 --> 00:31:53,830
Before this year's summer collection

823
00:31:53,830 --> 00:31:54,510
is launched,

824
00:31:54,510 --> 00:31:56,160
we can open two branch stores.

825
00:31:56,160 --> 00:31:57,160
The managers for them

826
00:31:57,160 --> 00:31:59,200
will be selected from current staff.

827
00:31:59,200 --> 00:32:00,330
Just keep an eye out.

828
00:32:00,640 --> 00:32:00,970
Okay.

829
00:32:01,200 --> 00:32:02,400
I share the same view.

830
00:32:02,720 --> 00:32:05,650
Where do you think
we should place the branch stores?

831
00:32:05,920 --> 00:32:07,200
Shengcheng and Longcheng.

832
00:32:07,200 --> 00:32:08,310
One store in each city.

833
00:32:08,310 --> 00:32:09,110
The new ones will have the same

834
00:32:09,110 --> 00:32:10,480
specifications as the existing ones.

835
00:32:10,480 --> 00:32:11,610
Exactly identical.

836
00:32:11,920 --> 00:32:13,480
Before the summer collection is out,

837
00:32:13,480 --> 00:32:14,960
they'll be open for business, right?

838
00:32:14,960 --> 00:32:15,560
By the way,

839
00:32:15,590 --> 00:32:17,270
how's the summer collection coming along?

840
00:32:17,270 --> 00:32:18,070
Wait a second.

841
00:32:24,440 --> 00:32:25,170
Here you are.

842
00:32:25,640 --> 00:32:26,900
One more catalog here.

843
00:32:34,960 --> 00:32:36,290
The designs are not bad.

844
00:32:36,440 --> 00:32:37,240
But I think

845
00:32:37,240 --> 00:32:38,400
we can add in

846
00:32:38,400 --> 00:32:39,640
some sporty elements

847
00:32:39,920 --> 00:32:41,380
to go with the Asian Games.

848
00:32:41,510 --> 00:32:41,910
Got it.

849
00:32:43,310 --> 00:32:43,720
Also,

850
00:32:44,000 --> 00:32:45,240
design a series

851
00:32:45,310 --> 00:32:47,200
of special outfits

852
00:32:47,510 --> 00:32:50,030
and make them a limited edition
for the Asian Games.

853
00:32:50,030 --> 00:32:51,310
The mighty spirit of Asia, right?

854
00:32:51,310 --> 00:32:52,310
Limited edition?

855
00:32:53,270 --> 00:32:54,000
What is that?

856
00:32:54,640 --> 00:32:56,100
By that, I mean we will only

857
00:32:57,310 --> 00:32:58,440
sell 10,000 pieces.

858
00:32:59,800 --> 00:33:02,060
Xia, you're really full of clever ideas.

859
00:33:07,400 --> 00:33:08,460
It's finally done.

860
00:33:08,720 --> 00:33:10,000
In fact,
the renovation of the two dinning halls

861
00:33:10,000 --> 00:33:11,110
was finished long ago.

862
00:33:11,110 --> 00:33:12,110
But we had to wait
till they were inspected

863
00:33:12,110 --> 00:33:13,640
together with the larger corporates' works

864
00:33:13,640 --> 00:33:15,040
to get the final payment.

865
00:33:15,350 --> 00:33:16,160
You know what, Xiaolan?

866
00:33:16,160 --> 00:33:17,200
In the recent two months,

867
00:33:17,200 --> 00:33:18,270
calls have been flooding in

868
00:33:18,270 --> 00:33:19,680
from customers requiring

869
00:33:19,680 --> 00:33:21,540
Yuanhui's renovation services.

870
00:33:22,070 --> 00:33:23,680
Yuanhui has really made a name

871
00:33:23,680 --> 00:33:25,140
for itself in Shengcheng.

872
00:33:25,680 --> 00:33:26,880
With steady business

873
00:33:26,920 --> 00:33:28,780
and the franchise fees from Luna,

874
00:33:28,960 --> 00:33:30,720
we can start building a materials center!

875
00:33:30,720 --> 00:33:32,240
This place looks great to me.

876
00:33:32,240 --> 00:33:33,640
According to Xiaolan, we should choose

877
00:33:33,640 --> 00:33:35,200
a location with relevant distribution hubs

878
00:33:35,200 --> 00:33:36,480
in the vicinity.

879
00:33:36,750 --> 00:33:38,030
I've noticed
that Uncle Yong kept going to this place

880
00:33:38,030 --> 00:33:39,030
when he did renovation projects.

881
00:33:39,030 --> 00:33:41,200
There should be relevant shops around.

882
00:33:41,200 --> 00:33:42,350
I also think it's a good place.

883
00:33:42,350 --> 00:33:43,000
There are

884
00:33:43,000 --> 00:33:44,460
wide roads front and back,

885
00:33:44,550 --> 00:33:45,720
making it convenient for our big trucks

886
00:33:45,720 --> 00:33:47,120
to load and unload stuff.

887
00:33:47,200 --> 00:33:48,590
Yes, and most importantly,

888
00:33:48,590 --> 00:33:49,550
it provides a broad enough space

889
00:33:49,550 --> 00:33:50,800
for us to not only display products,

890
00:33:50,800 --> 00:33:51,580
but also store items,

891
00:33:51,580 --> 00:33:52,640
leading to high efficiency.

892
00:33:52,640 --> 00:33:53,510
Given that we are

893
00:33:53,510 --> 00:33:54,440
not suppliers,

894
00:33:54,440 --> 00:33:55,090
but distributors,

895
00:33:55,090 --> 00:33:56,050
we have to attract customers

896
00:33:56,050 --> 00:33:57,680
by offering good service and convenience.

897
00:33:57,680 --> 00:33:58,210
Xiaolan,

898
00:33:58,240 --> 00:33:59,240
what do you think?

899
00:34:00,030 --> 00:34:00,960
What do I think?

900
00:34:02,130 --> 00:34:03,610
I think you have really...

901
00:34:03,640 --> 00:34:04,680
hit your stride

902
00:34:04,680 --> 00:34:06,010
in doing business, Wei.

903
00:34:06,310 --> 00:34:07,110
You bet I have.

904
00:34:07,110 --> 00:34:07,510
I'm telling you,

905
00:34:07,510 --> 00:34:08,920
my brain here is now filled

906
00:34:08,920 --> 00:34:10,980
with wisdom and talent.

907
00:34:12,800 --> 00:34:14,060
There's one more thing

908
00:34:14,550 --> 00:34:16,010
I need to discuss with you.

909
00:34:17,030 --> 00:34:19,110
That is, I'd like to invite my uncle
to be a shareholder

910
00:34:19,110 --> 00:34:20,510
of the materials center.

911
00:34:21,150 --> 00:34:23,210
For one thing, this is a large project

912
00:34:23,280 --> 00:34:24,550
involving massive capital.

913
00:34:24,550 --> 00:34:25,110
One more helper

914
00:34:25,110 --> 00:34:26,310
means more strength.

915
00:34:26,710 --> 00:34:27,840
For another thing,

916
00:34:27,920 --> 00:34:30,000
my uncle is a renovation constractor.

917
00:34:30,000 --> 00:34:30,880
Sometimes he lands

918
00:34:30,880 --> 00:34:32,139
major deals on his own.

919
00:34:32,280 --> 00:34:33,070
If he becomes a shareholder,

920
00:34:33,070 --> 00:34:34,400
those deals will be ours as well.

921
00:34:34,400 --> 00:34:35,480
It'll be more convenient.

922
00:34:35,480 --> 00:34:36,480
What do you think?

923
00:34:36,800 --> 00:34:37,550
I agree with it.

924
00:34:37,550 --> 00:34:38,760
I would've brought that idea up

925
00:34:38,760 --> 00:34:39,820
if Xiaolan hadn't.

926
00:34:39,909 --> 00:34:40,790
Look, now,

927
00:34:40,909 --> 00:34:42,370
Sis Bai handles supplies,

928
00:34:42,510 --> 00:34:44,110
Xiaolan is charge of the big picture

929
00:34:44,110 --> 00:34:44,800
and marketing,

930
00:34:44,800 --> 00:34:45,510
and Uncle Yong

931
00:34:45,510 --> 00:34:46,800
brings in big orders.

932
00:34:47,120 --> 00:34:47,710
But look at me.

933
00:34:47,710 --> 00:34:48,710
All I can offer is a little money

934
00:34:48,710 --> 00:34:50,040
and no other resources.

935
00:34:50,510 --> 00:34:51,800
If Uncle Yong doesn't become

936
00:34:51,800 --> 00:34:52,710
a shareholder, I will be

937
00:34:52,710 --> 00:34:54,360
too embarrassed to take up a spot.

938
00:34:54,360 --> 00:34:55,560
I also agree with you.

939
00:34:56,000 --> 00:34:56,360
Good.

940
00:34:57,240 --> 00:34:58,000
Oh right, Xiaolan,

941
00:34:58,000 --> 00:34:59,070
have you come up with a name

942
00:34:59,070 --> 00:35:00,530
for the materials center?

943
00:35:01,320 --> 00:35:03,380
Say it if you already have one in mind.

944
00:35:03,880 --> 00:35:05,110
I did think of a name.

945
00:35:05,440 --> 00:35:07,000
The center can be called

946
00:35:07,190 --> 00:35:08,960
"Happy Home Materials."

947
00:35:09,190 --> 00:35:10,190
What do you think?

948
00:35:11,030 --> 00:35:11,800
Pretty good.

949
00:35:12,360 --> 00:35:13,820
It feels less commercial,

950
00:35:14,000 --> 00:35:15,060
and more personal.

951
00:35:15,400 --> 00:35:16,460
Let's go with that.

952
00:35:18,030 --> 00:35:18,490
Senior.

953
00:35:20,280 --> 00:35:22,480
I just came back from the police station.

954
00:35:22,480 --> 00:35:24,170
That case about neighborhood disputes

955
00:35:24,170 --> 00:35:24,670
was finally closed.

956
00:35:24,670 --> 00:35:25,500
Okay, I got it.

957
00:35:38,190 --> 00:35:38,710
Senior,

958
00:35:39,840 --> 00:35:40,670
any progress

959
00:35:41,110 --> 00:35:42,570
on the construction site?

960
00:35:47,840 --> 00:35:48,710
In this day and age,

961
00:35:48,710 --> 00:35:49,920
finding a hidden temp worker

962
00:35:49,920 --> 00:35:52,000
is like looking for a needle
in a haystack.

963
00:35:52,000 --> 00:35:53,190
Everyone who has made

964
00:35:53,190 --> 00:35:55,150
such a big mistake at work like he did

965
00:35:55,150 --> 00:35:57,010
would likely get scared and hide.

966
00:35:57,550 --> 00:35:58,880
Shi Kai was a good fella.

967
00:35:59,920 --> 00:36:01,780
It's a shame he had that accident.

968
00:36:03,280 --> 00:36:04,510
It was not an accident.

969
00:36:04,510 --> 00:36:05,170
Zhou Cheng.

970
00:36:12,360 --> 00:36:13,360
Here is a case

971
00:36:13,360 --> 00:36:14,800
about a trading company in Shengcheng.

972
00:36:14,800 --> 00:36:16,860
It's complex and somewhat connected

973
00:36:17,190 --> 00:36:17,990
to Hangcheng.

974
00:36:18,320 --> 00:36:19,440
Handling it will probably take

975
00:36:19,440 --> 00:36:21,480
tremendous time and effort from you.

976
00:36:21,480 --> 00:36:22,920
But once you nail it,

977
00:36:23,280 --> 00:36:24,590
that will be a great step up

978
00:36:24,590 --> 00:36:26,190
for both you and the law firm.

979
00:36:26,880 --> 00:36:28,280
Take a look at it quickly.

980
00:36:28,710 --> 00:36:29,960
Your girlfriend is running
a prosperous business.

981
00:36:29,960 --> 00:36:30,800
You shouldn't fall behind,

982
00:36:30,800 --> 00:36:31,280
right?

983
00:36:33,030 --> 00:36:34,000
It's a new year.

984
00:36:34,910 --> 00:36:35,570
Zhou Cheng,

985
00:36:37,440 --> 00:36:38,840
you need to look forward.

986
00:36:49,400 --> 00:36:50,510
-Cheers!
-Cheers!

987
00:36:54,550 --> 00:36:56,440
Hotpot in the cold.

988
00:36:56,800 --> 00:36:58,800
Seafood in the heat.

989
00:36:59,190 --> 00:37:01,230
A joy nothing can beat.

990
00:37:01,230 --> 00:37:03,400
Then what's to eat
when it's neither cold nor hot?

991
00:37:03,400 --> 00:37:04,480
I'm not telling you.

992
00:37:04,480 --> 00:37:05,010
Oh right.

993
00:37:05,360 --> 00:37:05,880
I heard news

994
00:37:05,880 --> 00:37:07,210
about Du Zhaohui today.

995
00:37:10,360 --> 00:37:11,220
What happened?

996
00:37:11,400 --> 00:37:12,660
I'm being serious now.

997
00:37:13,550 --> 00:37:14,450
Do you remember

998
00:37:14,760 --> 00:37:16,150
the massive crackdown on vice

999
00:37:16,150 --> 00:37:17,550
in Shengcheng last year?

1000
00:37:18,190 --> 00:37:19,480
Today, in the police station,

1001
00:37:19,480 --> 00:37:21,200
I heard that the whole thing was caused

1002
00:37:21,200 --> 00:37:22,080
by Du Zhaohui.

1003
00:37:22,110 --> 00:37:23,510
He reported the dance halls his family ran
for involvement

1004
00:37:23,510 --> 00:37:25,040
in illegal sexual service.

1005
00:37:25,710 --> 00:37:26,510
So that was

1006
00:37:26,510 --> 00:37:28,150
the serious business he set his mind to.

1007
00:37:28,150 --> 00:37:30,070
He can't do business in Shengcheng

1008
00:37:30,070 --> 00:37:32,400
without committing an act of allegiance.

1009
00:37:32,400 --> 00:37:33,670
Therefore, he reported

1010
00:37:33,670 --> 00:37:34,930
such illicit business

1011
00:37:35,120 --> 00:37:36,960
to prove that he is pure in thought,

1012
00:37:36,960 --> 00:37:38,290
and upright in conduct.

1013
00:37:38,630 --> 00:37:39,190
I wonder

1014
00:37:39,190 --> 00:37:40,400
if he put on this show

1015
00:37:40,420 --> 00:37:42,350
for the government or for Xiaolan.

1016
00:37:46,110 --> 00:37:47,440
Are you stuffed or what?

1017
00:37:47,800 --> 00:37:48,710
I'm stuffed.

1018
00:37:48,710 --> 00:37:49,510
I was just joking.

1019
00:37:49,510 --> 00:37:50,370
Check, please!

1020
00:37:51,070 --> 00:37:52,800
Hello, bring me the check please!

1021
00:37:52,800 --> 00:37:53,280
Sir!

1022
00:37:53,400 --> 00:37:55,280
Qiang, get the check for this table.

1023
00:37:55,280 --> 00:37:56,400
Come carry the items!

1024
00:37:56,400 --> 00:37:57,160
Coming!

1025
00:38:01,630 --> 00:38:02,550
You...

1026
00:38:04,030 --> 00:38:04,480
You...

1027
00:38:04,480 --> 00:38:05,010
It's you,

1028
00:38:05,320 --> 00:38:07,110
the man who fixed my arm!

1029
00:38:08,440 --> 00:38:09,280
I remember now.

1030
00:38:09,280 --> 00:38:10,150
He's that thief!

1031
00:38:10,150 --> 00:38:11,190
He's not the thief.

1032
00:38:11,190 --> 00:38:12,920
No, I mean, he caught the thief.

1033
00:38:13,710 --> 00:38:14,770
All of you are here?

1034
00:38:15,370 --> 00:38:16,150
Good to see you.

1035
00:38:16,150 --> 00:38:17,400
Has your arm recovered?

1036
00:38:17,400 --> 00:38:18,070
Yes.

1037
00:38:18,110 --> 00:38:19,280
It's been a long time, right?

1038
00:38:19,280 --> 00:38:20,840
Didn't expect to run into you here.

1039
00:38:20,840 --> 00:38:22,700
None of you will pay for this meal.

1040
00:38:22,760 --> 00:38:23,360
It's on me.

1041
00:38:23,630 --> 00:38:24,090
Well...

1042
00:38:24,280 --> 00:38:25,510
Is this your restaurant?

1043
00:38:25,510 --> 00:38:26,920
Yes, as a matter of fact, it is.

1044
00:38:26,920 --> 00:38:28,110
That's Qiang, a good friend of mine.

1045
00:38:26,970 --> 00:38:31,470
♪ I'm never tired by your side
during this long journey ♪

1046
00:38:28,190 --> 00:38:29,850
He also owns this restaurant.

1047
00:38:31,110 --> 00:38:32,510
I used to be a seaman.

1048
00:38:31,780 --> 00:38:36,970
♪ We walk through
every leg of it together ♪

1049
00:38:32,800 --> 00:38:33,230
Now,

1050
00:38:33,320 --> 00:38:34,400
I'm done drifting around.

1051
00:38:34,400 --> 00:38:35,880
That's why I'm running this restaurant
with my friend.

1052
00:38:35,880 --> 00:38:37,000
Do come often, guys.

1053
00:38:37,000 --> 00:38:37,800
There are many special offers.

1054
00:38:37,500 --> 00:38:39,570
♪ As I climb over a peak ♪

1055
00:38:38,360 --> 00:38:38,710
Thanks.

1056
00:38:38,710 --> 00:38:39,600
-Thanks.
-Thanks.

1057
00:38:39,600 --> 00:38:42,170
♪ Another peak appears before my eyes ♪

1058
00:38:39,710 --> 00:38:41,280
What should we call you?

1059
00:38:42,590 --> 00:38:43,480
My name is Pan Baohua.

1060
00:38:42,660 --> 00:38:44,190
♪ Keep the goals high ♪

1061
00:38:44,070 --> 00:38:45,070
People usually call me San.

1062
00:38:44,220 --> 00:38:47,420
♪ Let your ideals always lead the way ♪

1063
00:38:46,440 --> 00:38:47,480
Nice to meet you, San.

1064
00:38:47,480 --> 00:38:48,290
My name is Bai Zhenzhu.

1065
00:38:48,290 --> 00:38:50,280
♪ Moments of joy and sorrow ♪

1066
00:38:49,670 --> 00:38:50,110
White

1067
00:38:50,300 --> 00:38:52,990
♪ Swirl around us ♪

1068
00:38:52,500 --> 00:38:53,830
You're from Bai Martial Arts School,
right?

1069
00:38:53,400 --> 00:38:56,430
♪ Admiring snow in the wind
and flowers in the fog ♪

1070
00:38:54,630 --> 00:38:55,190
Right.

1071
00:38:55,800 --> 00:38:57,070
You've heard of Bai Martial Arts School?

1072
00:38:56,460 --> 00:38:58,460
♪ Let's spin with joy ♪

1073
00:38:57,510 --> 00:38:58,280
Yes, as it is known to

1074
00:38:58,280 --> 00:38:59,480
everyone who practices martial arts.

1075
00:38:58,480 --> 00:39:00,210
♪ Don't hinge on petty things ♪

1076
00:38:59,920 --> 00:39:00,920
You've practiced martial arts?

1077
00:39:00,230 --> 00:39:01,610
♪ Savor the happiness ♪

1078
00:39:01,360 --> 00:39:02,230
We must have

1079
00:39:01,640 --> 00:39:03,640
♪ Around you every day ♪

1080
00:39:02,360 --> 00:39:03,660
a friendly fight one day.

1081
00:39:03,660 --> 00:39:05,520
♪ I hope you still believe ♪

1082
00:39:03,710 --> 00:39:04,440
Definitely.

1083
00:39:05,000 --> 00:39:05,960
Nice to make your acquaintance today.

1084
00:39:05,600 --> 00:39:09,420
♪ Beautiful scenes and happy times
are not far away ♪

1085
00:39:06,190 --> 00:39:07,070
This meal is on me.

1086
00:39:07,070 --> 00:39:08,150
Do come more often, guys.

1087
00:39:08,150 --> 00:39:09,070
Sure. Thanks.

1088
00:39:09,070 --> 00:39:09,580
Thanks.

1089
00:39:09,440 --> 00:39:11,630
♪ I'll use laughter ♪

1090
00:39:09,710 --> 00:39:10,710
We're leaving then.

1091
00:39:10,710 --> 00:39:11,240
Let's go.

1092
00:39:11,650 --> 00:39:14,330
♪ To bury all the pain ♪

1093
00:39:11,760 --> 00:39:12,290
Let's go.

1094
00:39:13,030 --> 00:39:13,590
Take care.

1095
00:39:13,590 --> 00:39:14,150
Don't leave anything behind.

1096
00:39:14,150 --> 00:39:14,510
See you later.

1097
00:39:14,350 --> 00:39:17,030
♪ I don't care for the raindrops ♪

1098
00:39:16,000 --> 00:39:16,530
Take care

1099
00:39:17,050 --> 00:39:19,620
♪ As I'm determined to march forward ♪

1100
00:39:18,150 --> 00:39:19,590
The clams tasted really good.

1101
00:39:19,590 --> 00:39:20,190
Good, huh?

1102
00:39:20,800 --> 00:39:22,000
Qiang, pack a portion of clams to go!

1103
00:39:22,000 --> 00:39:22,630
Sis Bai,

1104
00:39:23,080 --> 00:39:24,290
not full yet, are you?

1105
00:39:24,320 --> 00:39:25,150
I-I am full.

1106
00:39:25,230 --> 00:39:26,230
We'll come again.

1107
00:39:27,040 --> 00:39:27,600
Bye!

1108
00:39:27,630 --> 00:39:28,840
Okay. Take care.

1109
00:39:32,650 --> 00:39:33,760
I heard the business

1110
00:39:33,760 --> 00:39:35,710
of Xiaolan's store is booming, isn't it?

1111
00:39:35,710 --> 00:39:36,360
Yes, it is.

1112
00:39:36,710 --> 00:39:38,280
I'm told there will be branch stores.

1113
00:39:38,280 --> 00:39:39,190
Really?

1114
00:39:40,840 --> 00:39:41,280
Mom.

1115
00:39:42,440 --> 00:39:43,700
You're back, Xiaolan.

1116
00:39:44,150 --> 00:39:45,480
I heard from your mother

1117
00:39:46,030 --> 00:39:48,030
that you're opening branch stores.

1118
00:39:48,960 --> 00:39:49,490
Yes, I am.

1119
00:39:50,400 --> 00:39:51,800
So there will be new staff

1120
00:39:52,030 --> 00:39:53,690
and training sessions again?

1121
00:39:54,590 --> 00:39:56,850
I've really invited trouble, haven't I?

1122
00:39:57,710 --> 00:39:58,550
I want to quit.

1123
00:39:59,440 --> 00:40:01,360
But we're out of options.

1124
00:40:01,760 --> 00:40:03,420
No one but you is up to the task.

1125
00:40:04,710 --> 00:40:05,550
Granny Yu,

1126
00:40:05,800 --> 00:40:06,670
you'll be in charge

1127
00:40:06,670 --> 00:40:08,000
of training Luna staff

1128
00:40:08,030 --> 00:40:09,590
in the future.

1129
00:40:10,030 --> 00:40:11,030
After all, there will be

1130
00:40:11,030 --> 00:40:12,360
more and more Luna stores.

1131
00:40:12,360 --> 00:40:13,550
Each and every staffer

1132
00:40:13,550 --> 00:40:15,040
at Luna franchises

1133
00:40:15,070 --> 00:40:17,070
will have to be trained by you first.

1134
00:40:18,370 --> 00:40:19,930
How many franchise stores

1135
00:40:19,960 --> 00:40:21,020
do you plan to open?

1136
00:40:21,440 --> 00:40:22,500
This many in a year.

1137
00:40:22,800 --> 00:40:23,530
Five stores?

1138
00:40:24,920 --> 00:40:25,920
Fifty stores.

1139
00:40:26,480 --> 00:40:27,210
There will be

1140
00:40:27,510 --> 00:40:28,710
500 stores in 3 years.

1141
00:40:29,480 --> 00:40:30,760
Have you gone crazy?

1142
00:40:31,440 --> 00:40:32,200
Sorry.

1143
00:40:32,230 --> 00:40:34,230
This old lady won't play along.

1144
00:40:34,710 --> 00:40:36,450
Granny Yu...

1145
00:40:36,480 --> 00:40:37,480
Given the workload,

1146
00:40:37,480 --> 00:40:39,190
you must be straightforward

1147
00:40:39,440 --> 00:40:40,370
and name a price.

1148
00:40:40,590 --> 00:40:42,190
I'm a capitalist now.

1149
00:40:42,920 --> 00:40:44,800
Then I'll name a sky-high price.

1150
00:40:45,110 --> 00:40:46,170
Sure. Just name it.

1151
00:40:47,110 --> 00:40:48,110
I'll mull it over.

1152
00:40:48,320 --> 00:40:48,960
Okay.

1153
00:40:48,980 --> 00:40:50,190
Think carefully about it.

1154
00:40:50,190 --> 00:40:51,920
Look at this lassie and granny.

1155
00:40:54,590 --> 00:40:55,550
Please wait a moment.

1156
00:40:55,550 --> 00:40:57,810
The store will be open for business soon.

1157
00:40:58,510 --> 00:40:59,910
Hello, Ms. Xia, Mr. Chen.

1158
00:41:00,280 --> 00:41:00,970
Sorry.

1159
00:41:01,000 --> 00:41:02,400
The store will open soon.

1160
00:41:03,890 --> 00:41:04,590
You're here, Xiaolan.

1161
00:41:04,590 --> 00:41:04,960
Mom.

1162
00:41:05,630 --> 00:41:06,150
Mr. Chen, Ms. Xia.

1163
00:41:06,150 --> 00:41:06,680
Mrs. Liu.

1164
00:41:06,710 --> 00:41:07,240
Mr. Chen.

1165
00:41:08,110 --> 00:41:09,070
Before the store is open,

1166
00:41:09,070 --> 00:41:10,550
there's already a long queue outside.

1167
00:41:10,550 --> 00:41:12,760
They're all here for
the Asian Games limited edition clothing.

1168
00:41:12,760 --> 00:41:13,220
Ms. Xia.

1169
00:41:13,400 --> 00:41:13,930
Mr. Chen.

1170
00:41:14,280 --> 00:41:15,360
Only ten pieces are avaible

1171
00:41:15,360 --> 00:41:16,690
in each store every day.

1172
00:41:16,760 --> 00:41:18,760
They sell out within 5 minutes
after opening.

1173
00:41:18,760 --> 00:41:20,090
Should we provide more?

1174
00:41:20,280 --> 00:41:20,800
No.

1175
00:41:21,400 --> 00:41:23,400
Limited edition clothing
is a hunger marketing strategy.

1176
00:41:23,400 --> 00:41:24,550
If everyone can buy it,

1177
00:41:24,550 --> 00:41:25,920
the tactic won't work anymore.

1178
00:41:25,920 --> 00:41:26,510
Besides,

1179
00:41:26,840 --> 00:41:28,230
when the limited edition clothing
sells out,

1180
00:41:28,230 --> 00:41:30,290
we can offer similar items, can't we?

1181
00:41:34,150 --> 00:41:35,920
That shop across the street
has been leased?

1182
00:41:35,920 --> 00:41:36,800
Just a few days ago,

1183
00:41:36,800 --> 00:41:38,110
there was still a "For Rent" sign.

1184
00:41:38,110 --> 00:41:39,570
It has been rented out now.

1185
00:41:39,800 --> 00:41:41,730
I'm not sure what it sells, though.

1186
00:42:06,960 --> 00:42:08,030
Please come again.

1187
00:42:13,670 --> 00:42:14,400
Hello, Wang.

1188
00:42:14,480 --> 00:42:15,010
Mrs. Liu,

1189
00:42:15,320 --> 00:42:16,380
shall we leave now?

1190
00:42:16,590 --> 00:42:16,980
Sure.

1191
00:42:17,190 --> 00:42:18,360
Wait till I get changed.

1192
00:42:18,360 --> 00:42:18,760
Okay.

1193
00:42:24,710 --> 00:42:25,190
Wang.

1194
00:42:26,280 --> 00:42:26,800
Ms. Xia,

1195
00:42:27,230 --> 00:42:28,030
you're here too.

1196
00:42:28,030 --> 00:42:29,150
Where are you

1197
00:42:29,150 --> 00:42:29,800
taking my mother?
